Hi all,

Here I am again, after discussing with my boss about our logo.  
He is completely against overlapping the “my” over the “CORP”, but I made some changes to the logo according to your advice:

- bigger “my”;
- outline “CORP” in black;
- changed the “design e comunicação” typeface (as well as the whole tagline, since this one sounds better);
- reduced (R);
- some more changes I forgot to mention.

Here’s the new one. I would really appreciate your critiques about it.

